<item>
            <title>[LU-7931] Allow per-subtest setup/cleanup logic</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7931</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Back in 1.6/1.8 days we were able to run e.g. sanity as:&lt;br/&gt;
SETUP=setup CLEANUP=cleanup sh sanity.sh and that caused a remount after every subtest.&lt;br/&gt;
Other more involved proedures were possible to all from run_one() calls.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This all was lost somethime after run_one() migration to test-framework.sh&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Now the functionality is useful one so let&apos;s restore it.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
